  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nUsing `web/templates` as a template root with `TemplateRootBuildItem`, it's not adding the right `NativeImageResourceBuildItem`\r\n\r\nSee:\r\n```java\r\n2024-03-05 18:10:10,609 DEBUG [io.qua.qut.dep.QuteProcessor] (build-32) Produce template build items [filePath: WebResource/page1.html, fullPath: templates/WebResource/page1.html, originalPath: /Users/adamevin/workspace/redhat/quarkiverse/quarkus-web-bundler/integration-tests/target/classes/web/templates/WebResource/page1.html\r\n```\r\n\r\nin https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/qute/deployment/src/main/java/io/quarkus/qute/deployment/QuteProcessor.java#L3393\r\n\r\nit's adding the `fullPath` in the `NativeImageResourceBuildItem` which is `templates/WebResource/page1.html` it should be `web/templates/WebResource/page1.html`\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Quarkus version or git rev\r\n\r\n3.8.1\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is what I mentioned in https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-web-bundler/pull/165#pullrequestreview-1888549715\r\n\r\n",
